    <item>
      <title>Best Van Fans and Ventilation Setups</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/best-of/best-van-fans/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/best-of/best-van-fans/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Ventilation is not optional. It protects sleep quality, reduces mold risk, and keeps summer trips manageable.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;callout-shortcode&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;callout-title&#34;&gt;Quick Answer&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;callout-body&#34;&gt;Best all-around performance for full-time use: &lt;strong&gt;MaxxAir MaxxFan Deluxe 7500&lt;/strong&gt;. Best budget option: &lt;strong&gt;MaxxAir 4500&lt;/strong&gt; if you can live without premium controls.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;comparetable-wrap my-6&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;overflow-x-auto hidden md:block&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;table class=&#34;min-w-full border-collapse text-sm&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;        &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Product&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Best For&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Price&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Pros&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;Cons&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th class=&#34;border-b p-3 text-left&#34;&gt;CTA&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3 font-semibold&#34;&gt;MaxxAir MaxxFan Deluxe 7500&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Full-time comfort&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;$$&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Strong airflow and weather usability&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Higher upfront cost&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-neutral-300 bg-transparent text-neutral-500 opacity-70 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3 font-semibold&#34;&gt;MaxxAir 4500&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Budget builds&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;$$&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Reliable core airflow at lower price&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Fewer convenience features&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-neutral-300 bg-transparent text-neutral-500 opacity-70 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3 font-semibold&#34;&gt;CRL T-Vent Window (ProMaster)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Passive airflow boosts&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;$$$&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Better crossflow and condensation control&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Extra install complexity&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-neutral-300 bg-transparent text-neutral-500 opacity-70 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;space-y-3 md:hidden&#34;&gt;&lt;article class=&#34;rounded-lg border p-4&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3 class=&#34;text-base font-semibold&#34;&gt;MaxxAir MaxxFan Deluxe 7500&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;mt-2 text-sm&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Best For:&lt;/strong&gt; Full-time comfort&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>CRL T-Vent Windows for ProMaster Review</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/crl-t-vent-windows-for-promaster-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/crl-t-vent-windows-for-promaster-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;CRL T-Vent windows are one of the highest-impact upgrades for crossflow in ProMaster builds.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Major improvement to crossflow and comfort.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Better fresh-air management in hot conditions.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Works well with roof fan systems.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install requires confidence and precision cutting.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cost can feel high when combined with fan upgrades.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Builders in warm/humid climates.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Anyone frustrated by stagnant cabin air.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Yes, especially when paired with a quality roof fan.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>MaxxAir 4500 Review: Best Budget Roof Fan?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/maxxair-4500k-fan-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/maxxair-4500k-fan-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The MaxxAir 4500 is often the first fan budget builders consider, and for good reason.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Lower price than premium fan options.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Solid baseline airflow performance.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Simple controls that are easy to troubleshoot.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Fewer convenience features than higher-tier models.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Comfort in extreme climates may lag premium units.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Budget-first builders doing practical first conversions.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Weekend users and moderate climate travelers.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Yes. It remains a dependable value choice.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>MaxxAir MaxxFan Deluxe 7500 Review</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/maxxair-maxxfan-deluxe-7500k-review/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/maxxair-maxxfan-deluxe-7500k-review/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;For many full-time van lifers, a quality roof fan is one of the highest ROI upgrades.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;my-4 rounded-md border p-3 text-sm opacity-90&#34;&gt;Disclosure: Some links may be affiliate links. If you buy, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-transparent bg-neutral-900 text-white hover:bg-neutral-700 opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Pros&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;pros&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#pros&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Reliable airflow and strong comfort improvements.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Remote operation is useful during daily routines.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Better rain usability than basic fan models.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cons&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;cons&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#cons&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;More expensive than entry-level alternatives.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Install quality matters; poor sealing causes long-term headaches.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Who It’s For&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;who-its-for&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#who-its-for&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Full-time or frequent van users in varied climates.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Builders prioritizing sleep and moisture control.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Still Worth It?&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;still-worth-it&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#still-worth-it&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Yes. It remains one of the safest default choices in this category.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Ventilation Mistakes New Van Lifers Make</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/ventilation-mistakes-new-van-lifers-make/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/ventilation-mistakes-new-van-lifers-make/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Bad airflow causes more daily frustration than most first-time builders expect.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Mistake 1: No Crossflow Plan&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;mistake-1-no-crossflow-plan&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#mistake-1-no-crossflow-plan&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A roof fan alone is not enough. Pair extraction with side-window intake.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
